Package Models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Door
    Door is the item that is used to unlock the next level from the map
    Enemy
    Enemy represents enemies that attempt to hurt the player on the map
    Floor
    Floor represents floor tiles on the map grid
    Location
    Location of items on the map
    Loot
    Loot represents items on the map that the user can use to improve health, inventory, etc.
    Map
    Map is the object to represent the map and all of the items on the map
    Player
    Player represents player data and the player on the map
    Room  
    RoomTransitionTile
    The AbstractMapItem that represents the passage from one room to another.
    Session  
    Settings  
    Trap
    Trap represents traps on the map grid that do damage to the player
    Wall
    Wall represents walls on the map
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Player.PlayerDirection
    Directions that the player can move on the map grid
